    "translations": {
      "en": {
        "summary": "Imam al-Sadiq (AS) warns against attempting to contemplate the essence of Allah, as it leads only to confusion and deviation. He affirms the Quranic principle that Allah transcends human perception and cannot be grasped by vision or quantified by measurement. This teaching was given in a scholarly circle to redirect intellectual inquiry from God's unknowable essence to His signs and creation.",
        "key_terms": {
          "التفكر": "Contemplation/reflection - specifically about God's essence, which leads to deviation",
          "تيها": "Deviation/bewilderment - the result of attempting to comprehend the incomprehensible",
          "الأبصار": "Sights/visions - human perception that cannot encompass God"
        },
        "seo_question": "What does Imam al-Sadiq say about contemplating the essence of God?"
      },
      "ur": {
        "summary": "امام صادق علیہ السلام نے ذات الٰہی کے بارے میں تفکر سے منع فرمایا کیونکہ یہ حیرت کا باعث ہے۔",
        "key_terms": {
          "التفكر": "تفکر - ذات الٰہی کے بارے میں غور",
          "تيها": "حیرانی - گمراہی",
          "الأبصار": "آنکھیں - بصارت"
        },
        "seo_question": "امام صادق نے ذات خدا کے بارے میں تفکر کے بارے میں کیا فرمایا؟"
      },
      "tr": {
        "summary": "İmam Sadık (a.s.) Allah'ın zatı hakkında düşünmenin sapkınlığa yol açtığını ve O'nun insan algısını aştığını öğretmiştir.",
        "key_terms": {
          "التفكر": "Düşünme - Allah'ın zatı hakkında",
          "تيها": "Şaşkınlık",
          "الأبصار": "Gözler"
        },
        "seo_question": "İmam Sadık Allah'ın zatı hakkında düşünmek konusunda ne buyurmuştur?"
      },
      "fa": {
        "summary": "امام صادق علیه السلام از تفکر درباره ذات الهی نهی فرمود زیرا به حیرت می‌انجامد.",
        "key_terms": {
          "التفكر": "تفکر - درباره ذات خدا",
          "تيها": "حیرت - سرگردانی",
          "الأبصار": "چشم‌ها - بینایی"
        },
        "seo_question": "امام صادق درباره تفکر در ذات خدا چه فرمود؟"
      },
      "id": {
        "summary": "Imam al-Shadiq (as) melarang berpikir tentang zat Allah karena hanya menambah kesesatan.",
        "key_terms": {
          "التفكر": "Berpikir - tentang zat Allah",
          "تيها": "Kebingungan",
          "الأبصار": "Penglihatan"
        },
        "seo_question": "Apa kata Imam al-Shadiq tentang berpikir tentang zat Allah?"
      },
      "bn": {
        "summary": "ইমাম সাদিক (আ.) আল্লাহর সত্তা সম্পর্কে চিন্তা করতে নিষেধ করেছেন কারণ এটি বিভ্রান্তির দিকে নিয়ে যায়।",
        "key_terms": {
          "التفكر": "চিন্তা - আল্লাহর সত্তা সম্পর্কে",
          "تيها": "বিভ্রান্তি",
          "الأبصار": "দৃষ্টিসমূহ"
        },
        "seo_question": "ইমাম সাদিক আল্লাহর সত্তা সম্পর্কে চিন্তা করা সম্বন্ধে কী বলেছেন?"
      },
      "es": {
        "summary": "El Imam al-Sadiq (P) advierte contra la contemplación de la esencia de Dios, que solo lleva a la confusión.",
        "key_terms": {
          "التفكر": "Contemplación - sobre la esencia de Dios",
          "تيها": "Desviación",
          "الأبصار": "Las miradas"
        },
        "seo_question": "¿Qué dice el Imam al-Sadiq sobre contemplar la esencia de Dios?"
      },
      "fr": {
        "summary": "L'Imam al-Sadiq (P) met en garde contre la contemplation de l'essence divine, qui ne mène qu'à l'égarement.",
        "key_terms": {
          "التفكر": "La réflexion - sur l'essence de Dieu",
          "تيها": "L'égarement",
          "الأبصار": "Les regards"
        },
        "seo_question": "Que dit l'Imam al-Sadiq sur la contemplation de l'essence de Dieu ?"
